Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:06.02,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(283,0)\pos(358,297)}Nice \N Souther France
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barbara,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how about a Moscow Mule?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fritz,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,here is some juice for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fritz,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where is the "thank you" for your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Müller.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fritz!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will eventually get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new antique art dealership I \N started will eventually get rolling, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's still all very sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, suddenly I am able to live in this terrific place
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and also have a nice husband
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who makes tasty cocktails like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you sense anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The house next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times, I feel as though someone was \N watching us from that second floor window.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The house next door is vacant, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.19,0:01:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I heard this from Mr. Dautry,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who lives across the street from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.03,0:01:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heard what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.28,0:01:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a couple was slaughtered
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the house next door,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ever since then, there have been ghosts sighted there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.77,0:01:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is wrong, Michael?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you actually believe that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring the car out front.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.  Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think sometimes we should go \N out just by ourselves, as a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt we will need a bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure Fritz will get \N used to you more quickly that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that is exactly my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:39.40,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,101)\pos(352,312)}Happy Holidays
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, detective, what did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's start with Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police are after him as the \N main suspect in the Fortners' homicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, his current whereabouts are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he was first taken in for questioning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma reportedly said something along these lines:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the boy whose life he saved \N ten years ago had been on the run
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ever since he murdered the director of \N Eisler Memorial Hospital and two others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy's name was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later on, Johan showed up as a young adult
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and committed murder again, \N this time right in front of Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the daughter of the murdered couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she is also still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is Mr. Messner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I traced him to Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened about two months ago.  \N He was stabbed multiple times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said he got caught up in a conflict over drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Messner was my partner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I was with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Messner was dismissed from \N the force for his involvement with drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:05:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who took Messner under \N his wing was a man called "The Baby."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is a powerful figure in a fascist organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This past winter, there was a series of arson \N cases in Frankfurt's Turkish town, wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rumored that "The Baby" was \N the mastermind behind this incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that a certain Asian man prevented it from succeeding,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that the Asian man's name was Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this man was Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, one more thing... It's said that \N the fires were meant to be a festival
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to welcome a certain youth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the leader of the fascist organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the name of the boy \N whose life Dr. Tenma saved ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the youth that "The Baby" \N tried to set up as the organization's leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was also Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha, so that's the move you chose to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't my life
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like a chess piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when that phone call came...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my life was always about losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were detectives, my partner Messner and I
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,resold drugs that had been seized by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy on the other end of the line knew everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we wanted him to keep quiet, he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we would have to kill a certain couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fortners in Heidelberg...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we killed them, we'd be let off of the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That night,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was some journalist there was well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so Messner and I killed all three.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a huge sum was deposited into our accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The syndicate picked me up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after I quit the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, they appointed me to a \N really good post from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The money I earned got laundered without any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you met your wife, \N and washed your hands of the syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I allowed to leave so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the person at the \N other end of the line of that phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who deposited that \N large sum of money into my account?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who is controlling my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been protecting me all the way until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, will you wait on that move?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a harsh one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sweetie.  I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, please buy me toys!  Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fritz, how about tell your father, "I'm leaving"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his head is full of toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has the detective called?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto, the detective is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-you're...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the daughter of the Fortners, whom you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bodyguard, Roberto, is the one who killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching everything from the house next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:10:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto is a friend whom I can trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to get your revenge, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking this bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to stay here, go ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you have anyone you can trust, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mr. Müller?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Müller?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start the car. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching me for a long \N time from the house next door, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough to make me want to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I did it because I was threatened!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that unless I killed your parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be exposed for illegally reselling drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did with Messner... because we had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had not choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had no choice...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,choice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were great people...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really great...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father and mother
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,loved me from the bottom of their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was not their real daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my father and mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,really loved... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they were killed by scum like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barbara...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fritz...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barbara...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fritz...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is what it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fritz...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that child... called me, for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He called me "Dad."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now have things I don't want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barbara...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fritz...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every morning in Düsseldorf
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at 8:30, at that café...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I joined the syndicate, my boss gave me an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to act as though I was a normal \N business man with a regular morning schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every morning, a mother would \N pass in front of the café with her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my only contact with normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you ask that private detective to investigate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whereabouts of you and Tenma,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and what happened to my old partner, Messner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Messner was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was apparently killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked the detective to \N investigate his death further, in greater detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, there was a phone call from the detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are becoming strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.  Messner was a drug addict.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was no longer someone who would \N get caught up in a scuffle with the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the killer was not affiliated with the Frankfurt organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was with the Düsseldorf--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Düsseldorf?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, let's discuss this in more detail when we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the draft of his report.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"On Messner's death:"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The killer..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Roberto..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"who is he?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,understand what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like the bag back, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roberto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife and Fritz are relaxing somewhere close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-hey, what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put my wife on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should come back soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to your happy home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you lend me a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That gun can only be used at close distances.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, there are only four shots...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite everything, I'm still a former cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell the truth to the police, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not die, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will cover you from the vacant house next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fritz!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, look!  It's a fishing rod!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this child...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't stop talking about \N how he will have his father take him fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barbara...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Roberto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,several coworkers of his from \N the security company are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like something happened while we were out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coworkers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said there was no damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Roberto,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A glass pane was broken, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been a prank by \N one of the neighborhood children.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-where is the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The body of the detective that was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will make your wife and Fritz come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't make things more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, with this we can call \N say that nothing happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today was a peaceful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be peaceful from now on, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful girl she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are treating her extremely well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is a very important guest for a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the youth... was also Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan, Johan, Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish to live happily ever \N after with your wife and Fritz.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not let it rest at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nothing wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having me for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must bid you farewell today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to do with Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a happy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, when will you take me fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if it's sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer see ghosts, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have marvelous eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are very much like Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When can I see Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came without resisting
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you said I could meet Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is certainly true that he wants to see you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is living happily in Münich.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Münich?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do have marvelous eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really regret this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the only person left is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite everything, I'm still a former cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll reach your home soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to take Fritz...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fishing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it will be sunny...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.42,0:22:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that it will be.
